-----------------------------------------------
Usage: panda-cluster app COMMAND [arg...]
-----------------------------------------------
Follow any command with "help" for more information.

Panda-Cluster is built around a Cluster-App-Microservice (CAM) model for deployment,
allowing it to understand and gracefully manipulate clusters running in your AWS account.

An application is the second component of that model.  Several may run on a single
cluster together, and each is self-describing.  We make use of the huxley.cson manifest
file to specify service templates and

The following subcommands manipulate applications by accessing the specified cluster
and making use of its hook-server.

Sub-Commands:
   create
   delete
   push
